# type: textblock
#. type: textblock
#: ../src/guestfs-actions.pod:3076 ../fish/guestfish-actions.pod:2138
msgid ""
"If unavailable this is returned as an empty string C<\"\">.  Callers needing "
"to display something can use C<app_name> instead."
