# type: textblock
#. type: textblock
#: ../src/guestfs-actions.pod:3091 ../fish/guestfish-actions.pod:2153
msgid ""
"The release string of the application or package, for package managers that "
"use this.  If unavailable this is returned as an empty string C<\"\">."
